  "content": {
    "kind": "simple",
    "content": {
      "fragments": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "1",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I went down to the place where I knew she lay waiting"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "2",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Under the marble and the snow"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "3",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I said, Mother I'm frightened, the thunder and the lightning"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "4",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I'll never come through this alone"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "5",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "She said, I'll be with you, my shawl wrapped around you"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "6",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "My hand on your head when you go"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "7",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "And the night came on, it was very calm"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "8",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I wanted the night to go on and on"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "9",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "But she said, go back, go back to the world"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "10",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "We were fighting in Egypt when they signed this agreement"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "11",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "That nobody else had to die"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "12",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "There was this terrible sound, my father went down"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "13",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "With a terrible wound in his side"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "14",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "He said, try to go on, take my books, take my gun"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "15",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Remember, my son, how they lied"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "16",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "And the night comes on, it's very calm"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "17",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I'd like to pretend that my father was wrong"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "18",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "But you don't want to lie, not to the young"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "19",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "We were locked in this kitchen, I took to religion"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "20",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "And I wondered how long she would stay"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "21",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I needed so much to have nothing to touch"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "22",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I've always been greedy that way"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "23",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "But my son and my daughter climbed out of the water"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "24",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Crying, Papa, you promised to play"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "25",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "And they lead me away to the great surprise"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "26",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "It's Papa, don't peek, Papa, cover your eyes"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "27",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "And they hide, they hide in the world"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "28",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Now I look for her always, I'm lost in this calling"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "29",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I'm tied to the threads of some prayer"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "30",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Saying when will she summon me, when will she come to me"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "31",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "What must I do to prepare?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "32",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "When she bends to my longing like a willow, like a fountain"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "33",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "She stands in the luminous air"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "34",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "And the night comes on, it's very calm"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "35",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I lie in her arms and says when I'm gone"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "36",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I'll be yours, yours for a song"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "37",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Now the crickets are singing, the vesper bells ringing"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "38",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "The cat's curled asleep in his chair"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "39",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I'll go down to Bill's Bar, I can make it that far"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "40",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "And I'll see if my friends are still there"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "41",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Yes, and here's to the few, who forgive what you do"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "42",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "And the fewer who don't even care"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "43",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "And the night comes on, it's very calm"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "44",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "I want to cross over, I want to go home"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "lineBreak"
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "id": "45",
          "tokens": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "But she says, Go back, go back to the world"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
